{"tid":1333765,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"填詞人林律希逝世    《民主會戰勝歸來》非六四/城邦之歌  係香港之歌","createTime":"2019-07-19T23:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T00:29:16.000Z","uid":28257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e21ef8c8c5f119510733d10c422bb9f6b30b9c95","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T23:59:33.000Z","msg":"其實呢首歌就最好代表現時香港的歌曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKwxgTEEO5c&amp;t=159s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPKwxgTEEO5c%26t%3D159s&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83JyNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=7e28dc67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKwxgTEEO5c&amp;t=159s</a><br />\n<br />\n白頭浪，默含淚光衝往世外。<br />\n黑眼睛，觀看歷史哀怨跌宕。<br />\n紅日降，正義藏在星宿背後。<br />\n誰在笑，長夜伴著罪惡放蕩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">萬劫不改的眼光，拿著帶鮮血憤恨。<br />\n用最浩瀚的聲唱和，</span><br />\n哪怕像螳螂横著臂，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對暴政猶如煉鋼。<br />\n為我港，我捨身去擋。</span><br />\n<br />\n天有光，夕陽在催促要靠岸。<br />\n風有聲，傾聽默想怎去破浪。<br />\n明或暗，信念如舊清澈恬靜。<br />\n寒或暖，赤了丹心流過血汗。<br />\n<br />\n萬勸不改的國邦，<br />\n拿著鐵腕與慾望。<br />\n磨了最惡的刀對望，<br />\n你已在悠悠長夜裏，<br />\n習慣宰殺如暴漢。<br />\n忘掉地獄的火，有多燙。<br />\n<br />\n*民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">護城長幡揚掛獅子山，</span><br />\n若化石仍殘存著愛，<br />\n一刻霸佔的青苔，<br />\n鋪天蓋，蓋不住世代。<br />\n民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n後有巨浪承接這變改。<br />\n若世上仍流傳著愛，<br />\n即使軟禁斗室內，<br />\n我自由，與天地 同在。<br />\n<br />\n萬劫不改的眼光，拿著帶鮮血<span style=\"color: red;\">絕望</span>。<br />\n用最浩瀚的音<span style=\"color: red;\">附和，</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我插下吾民旗幟，<br />\n黃雨衣護蔭萬傘，</span><br />\n浪與花，護擁於四方。<br />\n<br />\n*民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">護城長幡揚掛獅子山</span><br />\n若化石仍殘存著愛，<br />\n一刻霸佔的青苔，<br />\n鋪天蓋，蓋不住世代。<br />\n民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n後有巨浪承接這變改。<br />\n若世上仍流傳著愛，<br />\n即使永葬尺丈土下，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我凌魂，與香港 同在。</span><br />\n<br />\n*民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n民主會戰勝歸來，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">護城長幡揚掛獅子山，</span><br />\n若化石仍殘存著愛，<br />\n一刻霸佔的青苔，<br />\n鋪天蓋，蓋不住世代。"},{"pid":"2dbc853666c0c22f871aff49b9ed3c35d84d7455","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">即使永葬尺丈土下</span>"},{"pid":"6e90c4a82b199f423699fb42d7ee5daa3bc513bf","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dbc853666c0c22f871aff49b9ed3c35d84d7455","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">即使永葬尺丈土下</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:04:44.000Z","msg":"red]即使永葬尺土下[/red]"},{"pid":"bc114a4f2b2b605407571d3a7a3e8c0d826511cc","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e90c4a82b199f423699fb42d7ee5daa3bc513bf","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dbc853666c0c22f871aff49b9ed3c35d84d7455","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">即使永葬尺丈土下</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:04:44.000Z","msg":"red]即使永葬尺土下[/red]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:05:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">即使永葬尺土下</span>"},{"pid":"167224f5601d947643015d118ca053576113c70d","tid":1333765,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}